553
00:24:28,073 --> 00:24:30,160
- People are now realizing that they want

554
00:24:30,160 --> 00:24:31,810
to record their lives.

555
00:24:31,810 --> 00:24:36,140
In a way, it's kind of enhancing
the love of photography.

556
00:24:36,140 --> 00:24:37,940
Went to Vietnam two or three times,

557
00:24:37,940 --> 00:24:39,870
but it wasn't until 1968

558
00:24:39,870 --> 00:24:43,480
did I come up against a real opportunity

559
00:24:43,480 --> 00:24:46,733
to stay in a battle for nearly two weeks.

560
00:24:47,570 --> 00:24:50,590
This picture here, I
call it my crucifixion.

561
00:24:50,590 --> 00:24:52,050
I put my cameras down.

562
00:24:52,050 --> 00:24:53,970
I said to one of the
soldiers, "Look after these."

563
00:24:53,970 --> 00:24:56,010
I had him on my shoulders, and I ran away.

564
00:24:56,010 --> 00:24:57,340
I was 31 years old,

565
00:24:57,340 --> 00:24:59,080
and I was strong as a lion, you know.

